Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:01.60,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Doppio...{Line 2 through 4 are copied from the 26 script. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:07.37,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Have you already forgotten that I gave you a portion of my King Crimson's ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:11.57,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Now is the time to use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:15.66,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,You have King Crimson's arms and Epitaph at your disposal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:19.74,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Calm yourself and watch for any movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.16,0:00:26.21,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Then try your best to predict \Nanything that could happen around you. {repeated "movements"}
Comment: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:30.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Opening
Comment: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:02.05,Main,,0,0,0,,B
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:08.39,Title Part 5,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(402,394)\pos(107,923)\fs60}Episodio 27  King Crimson vs. Metallica
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:06.77,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Look carefully and predict anything that could happen... {again, repeated "movement". Altered to match line 7}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:08.81,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Look ten seconds forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:14.48,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,B-Birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:17.78,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,The birds flew away like in my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:28.75,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,B-Boss!\N I just saw him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:32.29,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,In the vision Epitaph showed me,\N he conceals himself ten seconds from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:37.13,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I saw something in the shape of a human \Nblending into the rocks in the background!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.68,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,B-But right now I can't see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:42.34,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I can't see him with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:43.85,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,That's Risotto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:47.47,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,He's concealing himself through unknown means.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:48.85,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:52.81,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,You may not be able to see him with your eyes, \Nbut you can with your visions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:57.53,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Look a few seconds into the future\N to see how he's going to attack you, Doppio!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.70,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Th-There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:01.61,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,H-He moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.87,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:12.12,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I-I have a situation, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:16.34,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,In ten seconds, s-scissors are \Ngoing to b-burst out of my throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:18.38,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Calm yourself, Doppio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:21.93,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,What you witnessed was not your death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:25.72,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Risotto was a hitman in my organization\N whom no one could find.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:28.06,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Brace yourself for the pain\N you are about to endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:31.85,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Watch carefully for how he's going to attack you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:35.23,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,...just a few seconds in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:38.15,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,The fact that he's drawing near me, Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:41.36,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,...tells me he definitely doesn't have \Na remote-controlled Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:46.28,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Th-The vision showed scissors stuck inside my throat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:50.62,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Are you telling me the future can't be changed, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:51.71,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:55.00,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen the vision, \Nyou must brace yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:59.17,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,It is an inevitability that you will have \Na pair of scissors stuck in your throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:00.67,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,But see through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:03.38,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,See through his attack and act accordingly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:06.22,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,If you see through his methods, \Nyou can exploit his weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:12.73,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Then once you are within two meters of him, strike him with King Crimson's arms, Doppio!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.90,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.61,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,There you are! \NTake this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:19.65,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You're sloppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:25.24,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,But then again,\N in all my years of being a hitman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:28.74,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,...you're the first to land a blow this close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:30.75,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,How intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:32.25,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.54,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Your ability interests me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.46,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Even so, you'll meet your end!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:44.93,Thoughts,Doppio,0,0,0,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.43,Thoughts,Doppio,0,0,0,,How did he get them under my skin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:52.18,Thoughts,Doppio,0,0,0,,I'm sure he didn't lay even a single finger on me,\N and my mouth has been shut this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:55.73,Thoughts,Doppio,0,0,0,,A-And his Stand never even touched me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:58.44,Thoughts,Doppio,0,0,0,,But somehow the scissors \Nare coming out on their own!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:01.65,Thoughts,Doppio,0,0,0,,I-If I don't do something, \Nthey're going to tear my throat apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:03.36,Thoughts,Doppio,0,0,0,,I need to get them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:12.37,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,His actions just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:15.37,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I thought I would be able to \Nslice open his throat just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:18.67,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,...but it's like he knew I was\N going to put those scissors there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:21.96,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,He put his hand to his throat and defended himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.80,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Something is happening here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.22,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I need to be more careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:27.68,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,...so that my next attack will end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:31.60,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:42.36,Thoughts,Doppio,0,0,0,,Dammit... I still don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.69,Thoughts,Doppio,0,0,0,,The boss is gonna yell at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:47.78,Thoughts,Doppio,0,0,0,,It's still a mystery how he's \Nmaking himself disappear, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:53.04,Thoughts,Doppio,0,0,0,,B-But this damage... \NT-The strength in my legs is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:57.79,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Th-That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.46,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Doppio?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:02.67,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Did you see his attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:06.22,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:08.72,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,You weren't able to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.80,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Then move away from there immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:15.35,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Figure out where he is by\N forcing him to pursue you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.77,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Y-You asshole...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.19,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:26.19,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I'm going to see through him for sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:27.49,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:30.16,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I'll get within two meters of him no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:35.99,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,You just witnessed King Crimson's next vision, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.15,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.21,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,I asked you a question, Doppio!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.38,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:48.22,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,A right foot, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:53.93,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,In just a few seconds, \Nhe's gonna come at me with scissors again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.18,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I saw it flying off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:58.18,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,A foot is definitely about to go flying.{Argh Japanese vagueness. The scene is clearly set up so that both we and Diavolo are meant to think Doppio is referring to HIS OWN foot, but as we later see, it's RISOTTO's foot that actually gets severed. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.64,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,What did you just say, Doppio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:04.61,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,H-He's coming!\N I saw him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.19,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Flee immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:10.07,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Why didn't you run the moment \Nyou saw that vision, Doppio?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:13.57,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Risotto Nero, the hitman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:19.33,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,While his movements are careful, \Nhe's already made preparations to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.33,0:07:21.96,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I already can't put any strength into my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.54,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I don't think I can run.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.79,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Razor blades, scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:30.17,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,He's been waiting for me to lose all my strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:33.51,Thoughts,Diavolo,0,0,0,,This is bad.\N Doppio won't be able to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:37.43,Thoughts,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Even if I were to come out now,\N it would take at least ten seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:38.93,Thoughts,Diavolo,0,0,0,,This could be dire...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:42.19,Thoughts,Diavolo,0,0,0,,The damage he would sustain from\N losing a foot would be severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:45.65,Thoughts,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Somehow, I need to minimize the damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:48.57,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,I told you to flee from there immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:50.15,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,He's going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:53.53,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,But Boss, if I may interject...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:56.24,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,That's exactly why I shouldn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.83,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I've used up all my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:01.41,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,It'll be easier to figure this out if I don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:07.54,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I've been trying to figure out where he's been\N attacking me from with the razor blades and scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:10.05,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,But that's not going to help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.33,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:30.82,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,His ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:37.33,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,...allows him to create and control razor blades made from natural iron inside living creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:40.70,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,This frog and I being so worn out \Nis what tipped me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:48.34,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,You use your Stand ability to manipulate the iron within living creatures to create razor blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:53.84,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,And since the razor blades\N came out of the frog before me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:56.30,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,...you must be approaching from that direction! {That's the direction you're approaching me from!}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.97,Thoughts,Risotto,0,0,0,,Th-This man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:04.14,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Looks like the prediction was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.19,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,A foot did go flying off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:12.39,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Now the mystery behind the enemy's form is starting to unravel itself, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.65,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Huh? Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:18.91,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,That's strange. \NI could have sworn I had a phone on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.91,0:09:20.41,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Where did I drop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.62,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I mean, that's a frog...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.33,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Oh, there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:28.58,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,How the heck did I drop it down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:32.46,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,It's underneath these rocks and covered in sand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:36.93,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,This is awful! \NI need to report this to the boss as soon as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:39.35,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,D-Did it break?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:41.72,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Brrring ring ring ring ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:45.06,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Brrring ring ring ring ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.02,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:51.19,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Even though electronics are so \Nlight and small these days, they're really sturdy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:55.86,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Hello? Congratulate me, Boss. \NHe can't move anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.57,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.78,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Well done, Doppio.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.33,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,My Doppio...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.87,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Should I be the one to finish him off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:08.50,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Or should I wait until you get here, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:12.38,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,I want to personally ensure that \NRisotto Nero is finished off for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.05,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Leave him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:17.97,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Get closer, Doppio. \NGet within two meters of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.47,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,I will take it from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:22.68,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Until then, get closer to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:25.31,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Got it!\N I'll get closer, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:33.90,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Inside the wound where his foot was severed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.73,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,They're wriggling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:39.36,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Risotto's Stand is inside his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:42.82,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You have the power of precognition\N or something to that effect, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:47.00,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You had a good idea of \Nwhat would happen and how I would react.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:50.79,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,There's no other way you could have \Nseen through my position or means of attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:55.42,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I'm certain you were an incapable, \Ninexperienced runt when this fight began.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:58.88,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,But... just who are you at this moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:02.76,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You suddenly became filled with confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.93,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,And what's with that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.06,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Those aren't the eyes of a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.73,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,It's as if you're two people at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:17.32,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Could that be what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.28,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,No, I misspoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.11,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,It's not even that it "could" be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:23.78,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I'm much closer than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:27.95,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,...to the person I've been looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.55,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:43.30,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,It's been two years since we were turned into leashed pups, quivering with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:48.68,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You're definitely something more \Nthan what we've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:50.23,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:53.69,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I want to know what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.65,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I want to see your true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:12:00.69,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I want to know what you are when I kill you... no matter what!
Comment: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:03.07,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:13.75,Flashback,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Solido Naso... \NThat must be one of the boss's aliases.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:17.79,Flashback,Ghiaccio,0,0,0,,He wouldn't hide his daughter so quick if it weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:21.83,Flashback,Formaggio,0,0,0,,We came all the way out here\N just to waste our fucking time, dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:28.01,Flashback,Pesci,0,0,0,,But if we can get his daughter, \Nmaybe we can figure out who the boss is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.31,Flashback,Pesci,0,0,0,,Right, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:33.69,Flashback,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,We haven't been able to do shit \Nsince what happened to Sorbet and Gelato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:36.90,Flashback,Mellone,0,0,0,,I wonder who's guarding his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:40.23,Flashback,Mellone,0,0,0,,Pericolo isn't a Stand user, \Nso maybe Polpo or someone close to him?{This flashback irks me. Wouldn't Polpo have already died by this point? -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:45.20,Flashback,Illuso,0,0,0,,Maybe we should just go to Naples \Nand ask him in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.62,Flashback,Risotto,0,0,0,,Don't get yourselves worked up.{He uses "ukareru". This word comes up again in a few lines, so make sure the phrasing is consistent between the two. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:51.45,Flashback,Risotto,0,0,0,,It's times like these where we \Nneed to stay calm before taking action.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:56.63,Flashback,Risotto,0,0,0,,I understand how you all feel, \Nbut we need to bury what happened to Sorbet and Gelato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:59.59,Flashback,Risotto,0,0,0,,Failure means death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:06.51,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I'm riled up, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:10.10,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Whichever one of us gets too worked up\N is the one who will die. {And here we see the second "ukareru". Or, "ukareta", technically, but it's the same term. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:12.47,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,The foot I chopped off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:16.48,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I was right... Risotto Nero...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:19.69,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I see what your power is now! \NMagnetism!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:24.32,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,You're maintaining control from that distance\N with your Stand's ability to control magnetism!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.86,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,You took control of the iron inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:30.49,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,...and made me throw up razor blades \Nand scissors by creating them inside my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:34.45,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,You can make yourself disappear by \Ncovering yourself in iron powder...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:38.33,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,...and painting the scenery around you \Nto camouflage yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.54,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:45.17,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You may have figured out how \NMetallica works, but it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:49.89,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Because you're already finished...{The word he uses implies, like, finished in the sense of a piece of work that's been completed. He repeats this phrase several times throughout this fight, and I've gone with "finished" for all of them, so... pay attention to that. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.39,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:54.60,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,It's an element that exists everywhere in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:59.86,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Of course, it's in things such as \Nsand, spring water, and plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:13.24,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Iron also happens to be a \Nnaturally occurring material found in humans. {Iron isn't a compound.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:42.27,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Doppio?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:44.69,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,You predicted his movements!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:47.78,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,I will not allow you to sustain further damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:53.95,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:55.62,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:15:00.46,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Because you saw through my ability,\N my foot was severed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:03.54,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,But you're already finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:07.09,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,There's nothing you can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:12.97,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Large amounts of iron can be found in \Nvegetables like spinach and meats like liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:16.64,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,It's an important substance that\N runs through your bloodstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:21.06,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,What do you think happens when\N all iron in your body is expelled at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:25.07,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Simply put, your blood turns \Na horrible shade of yellow and you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:30.78,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,The iron in your blood captures the oxygen \Nthat enters your body when you breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:33.95,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,...and carries it throughout your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:39.79,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Without it, precious oxygen doesn't \Nreach your fingertips or your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:44.83,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Essentially, now that you've \Nbeen robbed of so much iron...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:49.51,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,...in spite of how hard you're breathing, \Nyour body isn't taking in any oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:53.97,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You'll be a walking corpse before you actually die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:55.97,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.43,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I wonder what I should do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:02.64,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Should I wait until you croak, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:05.11,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Since we seem to be short on time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.57,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,...should I go over there and finish you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.48,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,B-Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.49,0:16:11.40,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.78,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,They're near the mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:17.24,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,It's Buccellati! \NHe finally showed himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:20.45,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Narancia's there too, and... \NSo is Abbacchio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:23.50,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,What? Abbacchio's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.46,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,We're running out of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:27.96,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Doppio, finish him off with your next attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:30.92,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Predict Risotto's actions with your vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:32.88,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I'm already looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:37.05,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Risotto will come around my right side, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:40.02,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,He disappears! \NI can't see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.23,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:44.98,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,What do you see, Doppio?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.35,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:52.07,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I... I'm gonna turn the tables, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:53.78,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I'm gonna finish him off, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:57.41,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,In the few seconds I have before \Nmy vision becomes a reality...{Before the scene in my vision happens \Na few seconds from now...}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:17:00.58,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,...I'll blow his head off instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:03.71,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Just like I severed his foot earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.83,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,H-Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:11.05,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Don't do anything else, Doppio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.76,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,There's nothing more you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:17.22,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Listen well, Doppio. \NThis is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.30,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Don't waste any more energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.68,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,I'm heading there as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:25.44,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,It will be a few more seconds,\N but I will deal with Risotto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.90,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,A few seconds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.98,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,That's too late! \NHe'll attack me at any moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:31.48,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:37.16,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,If my full ability can reach you, \NI can erase the time you witnessed in your vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.07,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,But I'm the one who's about to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:40.12,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I'll kill him first!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:42.33,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Doppio! \NThis is the only way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.70,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,This is the only way to ensure your survival!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:47.42,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Your body has reached its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.42,0:17:50.75,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,I won't allow you to waste \Nany more energy on my behalf!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.55,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,You're going to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:57.09,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,You of all people could never\N locate him a second time!{These are some long-ass ten seconds... Are we actually on Namek? -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:01.81,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,...But what if I can, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:05.35,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,If I know where he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:10.52,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,If he's going to use his ability to try to steal even more iron from my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:14.98,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,H-Here he comes! \NHe's attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:17.11,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,The strength to pull...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:20.66,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,He should have the strength \Nto pull the iron from my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:23.37,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,The scalpel is pointing in the \Ndirection of the magnetic force!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:26.33,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,There you are, Risotto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.33,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I figured you would try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:34.59,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Magnetism pulls at iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:39.43,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You thought you could determine my location \Nby the direction of the iron being pulled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:42.89,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:48.56,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,...what you sensed was Metallica \Nproducing magnetism in my severed foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:51.40,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I left it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.40,0:18:56.03,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I learned from my mistake\N after you chopped off my foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:58.82,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I need to make the best of what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:03.37,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,There's hardly any oxygen left in your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:06.24,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You are completely finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:08.29,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You shouldn't even be able to move an inch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.33,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You're different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.33,0:19:15.71,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You're brimming with confidence, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.17,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,The excessive physical changes to your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:20.84,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,...and the way you talk to yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:22.80,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.81,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I finally figured out who you really are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:30.81,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Yes, I seem to recall something like this happening in 16th century Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:34.02,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,There exist people in this world \Nwith multiple personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:36.44,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,In some cases, the effects aren't just mental.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:41.91,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,There have reported cases of people's bodies, \Nphysiques, and even the language they speak changing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:48.20,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Originally, I thought you were\N the boss's most trusted subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.00,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,But you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.08,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,To think that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:53.88,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:58.50,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Once you die, \NI'll be able to see what your face truly looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:02.97,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,There's nothing you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.30,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I'm keeping my distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.68,0:20:06.35,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You have no strength to resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.85,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You're out of options!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.23,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.98,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I'm going to chop off your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.94,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,This is the end! \NTake this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:15.06,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Metallica!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:37.30,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:39.09,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Risotto...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:42.42,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,I told Doppio...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:46.93,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,...that you were no longer an enemy he could handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:48.89,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:51.85,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I knew it. \NThe enemy was already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:55.60,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,But I shot right through him! \NI got him good, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:58.06,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:04.36,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Since my blood has been robbed of iron\N and is no longer carrying oxygen through my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:09.58,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,...it's as if I weren't breathing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:13.83,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Which means the only signal \NAerosmith is tracking right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:16.29,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,How many enemies are there, Narancia?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:17.25,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Just one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:20.34,Main,Narancia,0,0,0,,Only one person is breathing on that cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:24.05,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,...is your breathing, Risotto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:34.89,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:39.31,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,This matches what Doppio \Nwitnessed in his vision, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:41.86,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I would have won...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:44.65,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I would have won for sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:48.37,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,But you had already thrown the scalpels at them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:50.08,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Boss...
