Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:46.69,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}We gangsters will raise a flag of rebellion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:04.54,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}The rage in our souls that erases any sense of fear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:11.50,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Has been with us since we swore to defy God's diabolical plan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:14.47,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Will retaliation mean curtains for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:19.18,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Casting aside a life in which our futures remained certain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:22.85,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}We challengers will stay gold
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.77,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Indeed, it's eye for an eye
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:31.23,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}And a requiem for the traitor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:37.20,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Together we will stand up against this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:39.78,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}In which despair breeds despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:42.91,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't care! I have no need for mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.91,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}If my body were to crumble to nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:49.54,Part 5 OP2 English b,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So too would my prayers fade away? Hell no!
